        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3746084476" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17392547611918765392">Tiptree is such a unique and riveting writer. I had only read her/theirs/his stories before this and enjoyed them, but loved seeing what Tiptree can do with a broader canvas. The story kept unfolding in these unpredictable ways, always suspenseful and well-crafted. The *many* characters are somehow all vivid and real despite not all getting the same amount of air time so to speak. I believed in all of them. There are mysteries within mysteries in this novel, and Tiptree&apos;s loose and vivid prose i</span>
  <span id="freeText17392547611918765392" style="display:none">Tiptree is such a unique and riveting writer. I had only read her/theirs/his stories before this and enjoyed them, but loved seeing what Tiptree can do with a broader canvas. The story kept unfolding in these unpredictable ways, always suspenseful and well-crafted. The *many* characters are somehow all vivid and real despite not all getting the same amount of air time so to speak. I believed in all of them. There are mysteries within mysteries in this novel, and Tiptree's loose and vivid prose is a pleasure. Can't wait to read more and more Tiptree. </span>
  <a data-text-id="17392547611918765392" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

